 ne mogu te toku učiti,

581
00:32:36,340 --> 00:32:39,160
 iako se moje rečenice zauzimaju za tebe,

582
00:32:39,160 --> 00:32:39,560
 ono,

583
00:32:39,560 --> 00:32:42,680
 kad želiš nekako gospodina zadržati tom rečenicom,

584
00:32:42,680 --> 00:32:45,560
 zadržati ga dojmom svojim koji si imao iskustvom,

585
00:32:45,560 --> 00:32:46,960
 ovaj,

586
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:48,420
 kako bih rekao,

587
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:50,140
 i možda je ta,

588
00:32:50,140 --> 00:32:50,380
 ono,

589
00:32:50,380 --> 00:32:53,400
 gdje je to nemogućnost da ga dokučiš do kraja,

590
00:32:53,400 --> 00:32:54,440
 a ipak,

591
00:32:54,440 --> 00:32:54,680
 ono,

592
00:32:54,680 --> 00:32:56,680
 pronalaziš te neke komadiće,

593
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,700
 kako bih rekao,

594
00:32:57,700 --> 00:32:59,460
 togo tajsta u svojim riječima,

595
00:32:59,460 --> 00:33:00,140
 i tako dalje,

596
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:00,640
 ali,

597
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:00,760
 evo,

598
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:01,160
 stvarno,

599
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:02,820
 a od ovi drugi koji imaju naziv,

600
00:33:02,820 --> 00:33:04,440
 lijepa mi je o čuvanju,

601
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,960
 to mi je u jednom trenutku,

602
00:33:05,960 --> 00:33:08,640
 ta riječ čuvati mi je bila otkriće,

603
00:33:08,640 --> 00:33:11,020
 kako dan živimo u vremenu,

604
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:13,060
 gdje imamo problema sa čuvanjem,

605
00:33:13,220 --> 00:33:14,300
 kako čuvat ljude,

606
00:33:14,300 --> 00:33:16,220
 ljudsku dušu,

607
00:33:16,220 --> 00:33:18,000
 čuvat ono što mi je rečeno,

608
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,200
 čuvat ono što su ljudi izrekli,

609
00:33:20,200 --> 00:33:22,360
 a možda se nisu dobro izrazili,

610
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:24,160
 čuvat osmijeh tuđi,

611
00:33:24,160 --> 00:33:25,220
 čuvat,

612
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:25,700
 ono,

613
00:33:25,700 --> 00:33:27,020
 tuđu možda nezgrapnost,

614
00:33:27,140 --> 00:33:27,860
 ili moment,

615
00:33:27,860 --> 00:33:30,160
 kad se ljudi nisu snašli,

616
00:33:30,160 --> 00:33:32,220
 jer mi je danas nekako previše,

617
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:34,200
 ja to zovem prostitucija,

618
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,600
 ne mislim o ovom nekom spolnom smislu,

619
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:38,620
 nego prostitucija je riječi,

620
00:33:38,620 --> 00:33:39,780
 tuđih osjećaja,

621
00:33:39,780 --> 00:33:40,620
 ono,

622
00:33:40,620 --> 00:33:43,040
 ruganje je postalo gotovo svakodnevna stvar,

623
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:45,400
 i ne znam uopće napraviti razliku,

624
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:45,980
 između, ne znam,

625
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:46,920
 satire,

626
00:33:46,920 --> 00:33:48,280
 ruganja,

627
00:33:48,280 --> 00:33:49,100
 podsmijeha,

628
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:50,040
 i takve neke stvari,

629
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:50,340
 dakle,

630
00:33:50,340 --> 00:33:51,680
 nešto što je baš potrebno,

631
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,620
 neki zdraviji humor,

632
00:33:52,620 --> 00:33:55,620
 i nečeg što zna jako raniti ljude,

633
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:56,220
 i tako dalje,

634
00:33:57,140 --> 00:33:57,660
 kažem,

635
00:33:57,660 --> 00:33:59,760
 ima, ima više možda tih nekih tekstova,

636
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:01,680
 koji su jednako sad simpatični,

637
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:02,500
 kad ih čitam,

638
00:34:02,500 --> 00:34:03,900
 ima jedan koji se zapisao,

639
00:34:03,900 --> 00:34:05,820
 sjećam se učkavaju ptiću mali,

640
00:34:05,820 --> 00:34:07,760
 u smislu,

641
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:08,000
 no,

642
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,780
 to mi je baš nešto sam,

643
00:34:09,780 --> 00:34:10,140
 onaj,

644
00:34:10,140 --> 00:34:10,840
 tad sam se,

645
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,780
 susreo sam s jednom osobom,

646
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:14,020
 i ono,

647
00:34:14,020 --> 00:34:14,640
 sjećam se,

648
00:34:14,640 --> 00:34:16,200
 da sam osjetio nekako,

649
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:16,480
 ono,

650
00:34:16,480 --> 00:34:17,840
 kao da bihila poletjet,

651
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:18,060
 ono,

652
00:34:18,060 --> 00:34:18,460
 napokon,

653
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:19,720
 biti slobodna osoba,

654
00:34:19,720 --> 00:34:20,340
 i tako dalje,

655
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:20,520
 ono,

656
00:34:20,520 --> 00:34:21,260
 nekako non stop,

657
00:34:21,580 --> 00:34:22,840
 isto ako nekih životnih kavez,

658
00:34:22,840 --> 00:34:25,160
 i istog nekog iskustva,

659
00:34:25,160 --> 00:34:26,520
 i onda nešto sam bio pročitao,

660
00:34:26,520 --> 00:34:27,640
 i to mi je nadošlo,

661
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:28,640
 ptiću mali,

662
00:34:28,640 --> 00:34:29,520
 hrabri se,

663
00:34:29,520 --> 00:34:29,880
 našto,

664
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:30,660
 poletjeti,

665
00:34:30,660 --> 00:34:31,120
 tako,

666
00:34:31,120 --> 00:34:33,100
 ima ražniji tekstova,

667
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:33,520
 ali Karim,

668
00:34:33,520 --> 00:34:35,600
 jako mi je zanimljivo sad čitati,

669
00:34:35,600 --> 00:34:36,180
 ono što si,

670
00:34:36,180 --> 00:34:37,140
 onaj,

671
00:34:37,140 --> 00:34:38,100
 prethodno bio spominjao,

672
00:34:38,100 --> 00:34:38,680
 ozrcalo,

673
00:34:38,680 --> 00:34:38,940
 jeli,

674
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,020
 i ogledalo,

675
00:34:40,020 --> 00:34:42,360
 baš mi je zanimljivo sad neke te stvari čitati,

676
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:42,540
 ono,

677
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:45,200
 gotovo me automatski me prebacio vrijeme,

678
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:46,140
 kad je nastajalo,

679
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:48,980
 upravo neka posebnost te knjige,

680
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,520
 jer što je sve to osobno dožiljeno i prožiljeno,

681
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:53,840
 bio nam je gost i Fran Nikola Juršić,

682
00:34:53,840 --> 00:34:55,080
 koji je isto izbacio knjigu,

683
00:34:55,080 --> 00:34:55,800
 ono,

684
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,880
 evo što si rekao,

685
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,180
 gledalo duše nekako,

686
00:34:59,180 --> 00:35:01,360
 baš nekako pomaže ljudima,

687
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:05,340
 koji možda nisu sami sposobni izrasti sve što im se događa u duši,

688
00:35:05,340 --> 00:35:08,020
 onda se oni pronalaze u takvim tekstojima.

689
00:35:08,020 --> 00:35:08,580
 Da, da.

690
00:35:08,580 --> 00:35:10,540
 Pa, jedna od,

691
00:35:10,540 --> 00:35:12,080
 definitiv jedna od stvari je,

692
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:14,300
 ja ću biti iskren,

693
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:17,520
 ja sam se dugo mučio to javno objavljivati.

694
00:35:17,520 --> 00:35:20,560
 Prvo, ja sam dio jedne zajednice

695
00:35:20,560 --> 00:35:22,920
 i mi fratri, naravno,

696
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:24,540
 kao i svaki drugi ljudi,

697
00:35:24,540 --> 00:35:25,300
 nekad znamo,

698
00:35:25,300 --> 00:35:26,720
 možda biti malo,

699
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:27,740
 da tako se izrazim,

700
00:35:27,740 --> 00:35:28,700
 možda grubo,

701
00:35:28,700 --> 00:35:31,160
 nemilosrdni jedni prema drugima

702
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,920
 i nekako ismijati,

703
00:35:32,920 --> 00:35:34,400
 ismijati, ne znam,

704
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:35,420
 neku umjetnost,

705
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,500
 način pisanja, izriča i tako dalje,

706
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:39,540
 što je sastavni dio života,

707
00:35:39,540 --> 00:35:41,000
 neke stvari u životu ne možemo izbiti.

708
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,140
 Ne mislim da je to nužno sad nešto loše,

709
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:44,220
 ali je tako.

710
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:47,300
 Ja sam se dugo mučio

711
00:35:47,300 --> 00:35:48,700
 izaći u javni prostor,

712
00:35:48,700 --> 00:35:51,740
 zbog svojih osobnih nekih obzira,

713
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:52,980
 kojih je bilo jako puno,

714
00:35:52,980 --> 00:35:56,260
 strahova i tog nekog osjećaja,

715
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:58,400
 šta ako me neko sastruže,

716
00:35:58,400 --> 00:35:59,840
 šta ako neko uzme to

717
00:35:59,840 --> 00:36:02,420
 i napadnete su šta ti pišeš,

718
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,180
 šta ti iznosiš,

719
00:36:03,180 --> 00:36:04,940
 šta ti kao nešto osjećaš,

720
00:36:04,940 --> 00:36:05,860
 tebi nešto, ne znam,

721
00:36:05,860 --> 00:36:07,400
 Bog govori ili,

722
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,500
 kako bih rekao,

723
00:36:08,500 --> 00:36:09,840
 ili nešto treće.

724
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,600
 Ja sam se puno mučio,

725
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:14,720
 ima jedna riječ koja isto meni je jako draga

726
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:16,300
 i ona se isto provlači dosta kroz kinzu,

727
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:17,180
 to je ranjivost.

728
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:19,180
 Mi smo stvarno ranjivi

729
00:36:19,180 --> 00:36:23,800
 i nekada tu ranjivost ne možemo pobjeći od nje.

730
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:27,120
 I meni je trebalo puno vremena

731
00:36:27,120 --> 00:36:29,980
 da uđem u taj neki,

732
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:30,640
 ja imam reći tako,

733
00:36:30,640 --> 00:36:31,520
 u obzor slobode,

734
00:36:31,520 --> 00:36:33,260
 u neko ozrače slobode,

735
00:36:33,260 --> 00:36:36,020
 ne da me nije briga šta neko govori,

736
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:38,020
 jer uvijek će ljudi govoriti,

737
00:36:38,020 --> 00:36:38,740
 komentirati,

738
00:36:38,740 --> 00:36:39,320
 tumačiti,

739
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:40,640
 to ne možemo izbjeći,

740
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:44,380
 ali da ja slobodno mogu stajati za svojih riječi.

741
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:48,120
 Dakle, da se ja ne plašim onoga što sam ja napisao

742
00:36:48,120 --> 00:36:50,920
 i ako bi me sutra neko rekao šta je ovo,

743
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:52,660
 da ja mogu reći šta je to.

744
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:54,640
 Dakle, to mi je baš,

745
00:36:54,640 --> 00:36:56,980
 baš mi je trebalo dugo razdoblje,

746
00:36:56,980 --> 00:36:58,880
 da to nekako se prelomi u meni,

747
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:00,160
 da to izađe van.

748
00:37:00,160 --> 00:37:01,320
 Naravno, danas,

749
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,960
 kako bih rekao,

750
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:05,680
 ljudi možda neki koji imaju dara,

751
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:06,780
 talenta za pisanje,

752
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:07,940
 možda zaziru od toga,

753
00:37:07,940 --> 00:37:10,300
 baš zbog tih obzira,

754
00:37:10,300 --> 00:37:12,040
 ne znam, strahova i tako dalje,

755
00:37:12,040 --> 00:37:13,300
 tuđih očiju,

756
00:37:13,300 --> 00:37:14,860
 koje nekad isto tako znaju biti,

757
00:37:14,860 --> 00:37:15,580
 ali nemalo sr,

758
00:37:15,580 --> 00:37:18,300
 nekad nešto pogledaju, pročitaju i tako dalje.

759
00:37:18,300 --> 00:37:21,640
 A kako bih rekao,

760
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:23,160
 a negdje drugdje ono,

761
00:37:23,160 --> 00:37:25,960
 taj strah od tog mogućeg,

762
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,360
 jel, komentara,

763
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:29,660
 koji nečalost nekad je,

764
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:31,540
 je osobitno na tim društvenim mrežama,

765
00:37:31,540 --> 00:37:33,420
 kad imate ljude koji vam komentiraju,

766
00:37:33,420 --> 00:37:34,900
 nema nime ni prezimena,

767
00:37:34,900 --> 00:37:36,540
 jako ružno,

768
00:37:36,540 --> 00:37:38,520
 i nekad mi se više poistovjetimo

769
00:37:38,520 --> 00:37:40,260
 s tim jednim negativnim komentarom,

770
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:41,840
 nego možda tisuću drugih,

771
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,320
 koji su vrlo pozitivni,

772
00:37:43,380 --> 00:37:45,200
 hrabrujući i poticajni i tako dalje.

773
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:46,200
 Ali,

774
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:47,260
 meni je taj moment,

775
00:37:47,260 --> 00:37:48,340
 kad sam ih shvatio,

776
00:37:48,340 --> 00:37:48,840
 jel,

777
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:51,240
 da je to nešto baš moje,

778
00:37:51,240 --> 00:37:52,080
 ono,

779
00:37:52,080 --> 00:37:54,660
 što je gospodin meni darovao,

780
00:37:54,660 --> 00:37:57,300
 što je dio mog tog iskustva,

781
00:37:57,300 --> 00:37:57,600
 jel,

782
00:37:57,600 --> 00:38:01,020
 i da ja to sad nemam problema podijeliti s drugima,

783
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:01,760
 da sam nemam,

784
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,200
 nemam sad više problema,

785
00:38:03,200 --> 00:38:05,340
 da sva čije oči gledaju to,

786
00:38:05,340 --> 00:38:07,380
 i oči koje će se možda natopiti suzama,

787
00:38:07,380 --> 00:38:09,600
 jer će naći neku lijekovitu misl,

788
00:38:09,600 --> 00:38:10,740
 lijekovitu riječ za sebe,

789
00:38:10,940 --> 00:38:12,000
 doni koji će, ono,

790
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,280
 možda zaklopiti kingu i reći,

791
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,540
 ono, šta on, šta mali,

792
00:38:14,540 --> 00:38:14,760
 jel.

793
00:38:14,760 --> 00:38:15,860
 Tako da,

794
00:38:15,860 --> 00:38:18,160
 i ovaj moment mi osobe,

795
00:38:18,160 --> 00:38:19,040
 bi to bio drag,

796
00:38:19,040 --> 00:38:21,180
 što su se meni javljali ljude,

797
00:38:21,180 --> 00:38:22,000
 evo sad isto vidim,

798
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,000
 na osobi to zadnjih možda tijan dana,

799
00:38:24,000 --> 00:38:25,280
 ono,

800
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:25,740
 napiše,

801
00:38:25,740 --> 00:38:27,580
 napiše ti osoba koja te nikad nije vidjela,

802
00:38:27,580 --> 00:38:27,900
 ne znam,

803
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:29,000
 iz Njemačke, Austrije,

804
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:32,060
 nekog drugog mjesta iz Hrvatske,

805
00:38:32,060 --> 00:38:32,780
 kaže,

806
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:34,020
 dušu sam isplakala.

807
00:38:34,020 --> 00:38:34,680
 Ono, mislim,

808
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:36,460
 samo ti se javi,

809
00:38:36,460 --> 00:38:36,960
 napiše,

810
00:38:36,960 --> 00:38:39,640
 nikad te neko nije vidio,

811
00:38:39,640 --> 00:38:41,260
 ali tu se pronađe,

812
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:43,540
 i tu pronađe neki dubliji smisao.

813
00:38:43,540 --> 00:38:44,180
 I to je meni,

814
00:38:44,180 --> 00:38:45,940
 to je meni nekako i teološki,

815
00:38:45,940 --> 00:38:46,380
 jer, ono,

816
00:38:46,380 --> 00:38:48,680
 mi baš imamo to i u Svetom pismu,

817
00:38:48,680 --> 00:38:50,160
 i ušlo je u liturgiju crkve,

818
00:38:50,160 --> 00:38:51,940
 njegove nas modrice izliječiše.

819
00:38:51,940 --> 00:38:53,140
 Dakle,

820
00:38:53,140 --> 00:38:55,700
 nas je gospodinova rana izliječila,

821
00:38:55,700 --> 00:38:56,480
 i ozdravila,

822
00:38:56,480 --> 00:38:59,140
 i te naše rane,

823
00:38:59,140 --> 00:39:00,180
 koje su nekako,

824
00:39:00,180 --> 00:39:02,120
 kad su stopljene s gospodinovim,

825
00:39:02,120 --> 00:39:04,600
 kako je to ljekovito za ljudske duše.

826
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:05,920
 Ja moram priznati da je meni,

827
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:06,940
 za me najbolji komentar,

828
00:39:06,940 --> 00:39:08,900
 lijepo je čuti komentar svakati,

829
00:39:08,900 --> 00:39:09,960
 čast, ovo vam je,

830
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,240
 super, ovo vam se super sviđa,

831
00:39:11,240 --> 00:39:12,160
 jao, kako ovo, dobro,

832
00:39:12,160 --> 00:39:13,140
 sve je to lijepo.

833
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:14,740
 Najbolji komentar,

834
00:39:14,740 --> 00:39:17,240
 je kad osoba reagira.

