1164
00:46:43,040 --> 00:46:43,260
 onda,

1165
00:46:43,260 --> 00:46:44,400
 ali onda nisam,

1166
00:46:44,400 --> 00:46:46,660
 baš dugo nisam bio dobio nikakav odgovor,

1167
00:46:46,920 --> 00:46:48,100
 mislim što negdje razumijem,

1168
00:46:48,100 --> 00:46:48,900
 jer ja sam nekako,

1169
00:46:48,900 --> 00:46:49,060
 ono,

1170
00:46:49,060 --> 00:46:49,320
 još,

1171
00:46:49,320 --> 00:46:50,180
 amo tako,

1172
00:46:50,180 --> 00:46:51,260
 nisam poznat,

1173
00:46:51,260 --> 00:46:51,560
 pa,

1174
00:46:51,560 --> 00:46:53,280
 ljudi su uvijek malo oprezni,

1175
00:46:53,280 --> 00:46:53,800
