1178
00:46:55,760 --> 00:46:56,980
 nisam neko poznat u ime,

1179
00:46:56,980 --> 00:46:57,200
 pa,

1180
00:46:57,200 --> 00:46:59,200
 da će se svako otimati sada za tebe,

1181
00:46:59,200 --> 00:47:02,580
 i ja sam na kraju odlučio tiskati to u vlastitoj nakladi,

1182
00:47:02,580 --> 00:47:05,620
 što malo otežava neke detalje,

1183
00:47:05,620 --> 00:47:07,000
 mnoge detalje otežava,

1184
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:08,040
 tako da,

1185
00:47:08,040 --> 00:47:08,480
 ovaj,

1186
00:47:08,480 --> 00:47:10,620
 drug čijek kad ti tiska nakladička kuća,

1187
00:47:10,680 --> 00:47:12,060
 onda oni to rješavaju sa,

1188
00:47:12,060 --> 00:47:13,380
 kako bih rekao,

1189
00:47:13,380 --> 00:47:16,020
 nekim drugim knjižarama i mjestima gdje to šalju,

1190
00:47:16,020 --> 00:47:17,200
 i kako uzmaju proviziju,

1191
00:47:17,200 --> 00:47:17,680
 i tako dalje,

1192
00:47:17,680 --> 00:47:20,620
 nisam baš dobar u tom ekonomskom dijelu priče,

1193
00:47:20,620 --> 00:47:21,560
 ali,

1194
00:47:21,560 --> 00:47:22,040
 ovaj,

1195
00:47:22,040 --> 00:47:23,860
 u svakom slučaju,

1196
00:47:23,860 --> 00:47:25,400
 mi smo nakon,

1197
00:47:25,400 --> 00:47:26,660
 sad izležen,

1198
00:47:26,660 --> 00:47:28,560
 nakon što je knjiga tiskana,

1199
00:47:28,560 --> 00:47:30,900
 na Instagramu smo otvorili jedan profil,

1200
00:47:30,900 --> 00:47:32,560
 koji se zove na zaogranu slabošću,

1201
00:47:32,560 --> 00:47:35,500
 i s obzirom da ja vrlo brzo se moram vratiti nazad,

1202
00:47:35,500 --> 00:47:36,460
