1204
00:47:37,340 --> 00:47:38,640
 ili rješava te stvari,

1205
00:47:38,640 --> 00:47:40,040
 ova urednica Marija,

1206
00:47:40,040 --> 00:47:42,080
 ona će voditi tu cijelu priču,

1207
00:47:42,080 --> 00:47:43,840
 mogu se javiti njoj,

1208
00:47:43,840 --> 00:47:44,660
 i bit će svi,

1209
00:47:44,660 --> 00:47:45,620
 kako bih rekao,

1210
00:47:45,620 --> 00:47:49,560
 svi potrebni podaci će biti na toj stranici za ogranu slabošću,

1211
00:47:49,560 --> 00:47:51,920
 ako se neko meni javi na moj Instagram profil,

1212
00:47:51,920 --> 00:47:52,680
 na moj broj,

1213
00:47:52,680 --> 00:47:53,500
 ja ću ih,

1214
00:47:53,500 --> 00:47:53,740
 ono,

1215
00:47:53,740 --> 00:47:54,660
