1216
00:47:54,660 --> 00:47:56,560
 a što se tiče Amerike i Kanade,

1217
00:47:56,560 --> 00:47:58,120
 kako bih rekao,

1218
00:47:58,120 --> 00:48:00,960
 ja ću vjerojatno poslati određeni broj knjiga tamo,

1219
00:48:00,960 --> 00:48:02,220
 ili nekoliko paketa,

1220
00:48:02,220 --> 00:48:02,840
 ja ću to,

1221
00:48:06,460 --> 00:48:07,520
 oko ovdje na području,

1222
00:48:07,520 --> 00:48:08,120
 jel, Europe,

1223
00:48:08,120 --> 00:48:09,160
 osobito Hrvatska,

1224
00:48:09,160 --> 00:48:10,040
 Bosna i Hercegovina,

1225
00:48:10,040 --> 00:48:12,140
 ili možda i Zapadna Europa,

1226
00:48:12,140 --> 00:48:13,460
 a kako bih rekao,

1227
00:48:13,460 --> 00:48:14,940
 Marija će voditi svu tu priču,

1228
00:48:14,940 --> 00:48:18,480
 a naravno pokušaj ćemo vidjeti kroz neko naredno vrijeme,

1229
00:48:18,480 --> 00:48:20,280
 to je sad nešto post,

1230
00:48:20,280 --> 00:48:21,660
 ili nakon ovoga svega,

1231
00:48:21,660 --> 00:48:25,440
 da određeni broj tih knjiga bude u različitim knjižarama,

1232
00:48:25,440 --> 00:48:26,160
 koje su,

1233
00:48:26,160 --> 00:48:27,580
 kako bih rekao,

1234
00:48:27,580 --> 00:48:29,040
 poznate po Hrvatskoj,

1235
00:48:29,040 --> 00:48:30,220
 i po Bosni i Hercegovini,

1236
00:48:30,220 --> 00:48:32,240
 ili u nekim čak samostanima,

1237
00:48:32,240 --> 00:48:33,860
 kućama molitve,

1238
00:48:33,960 --> 00:48:37,800
 dakle gdje ljudi vole imati i kupiti neku duhovnu literaturu,

1239
00:48:37,800 --> 00:48:40,600
 ali mislim da će taj proces biti malo sporiji,

1240
00:48:40,600 --> 00:48:42,020
 tako da evo...

1241
00:48:42,020 --> 00:48:43,500
 Da je ugovoro za početak,

1242
00:48:43,500 --> 00:48:45,580
 Instagram stranica Zagorun Slabuši.

1243
00:48:45,580 --> 00:48:47,100
 Tako je, tako je, to je to.

1244
00:48:47,100 --> 00:48:50,460
 Evo, vi ste već spomenuli da ste vi u Kanadi,

1245
00:48:50,460 --> 00:48:51,360
 na župi,

1246
00:48:51,360 --> 00:48:53,180
 kako je gore preko bare?

1247
00:48:53,180 --> 00:48:56,360
 Pa evo, ja sam sad,

1248
00:48:56,360 --> 00:48:58,260
 sad je osam mjeseci,

1249
00:48:58,260 --> 00:49:00,180
 kako sam u Montrealu,

1250
00:49:00,180 --> 00:49:03,360
 a sve ukupno sam na sjevenoameričkom kontinentu,

1251
00:49:03,960 --> 00:49:05,720
 četiri godine i osam mjeseci,

1252
00:49:05,720 --> 00:49:06,860
 je to skoro pet godina.

1253
00:49:06,860 --> 00:49:09,500
 Pa naravno,

1254
00:49:09,500 --> 00:49:13,860
 to je neki drugčiji stil i način života,

1255
00:49:13,860 --> 00:49:14,520
 barem meni.

1256
00:49:14,520 --> 00:49:16,420
 Možda neko se bolje uklopi,

1257
00:49:16,420 --> 00:49:17,160
 neko lošije.

1258
00:49:17,160 --> 00:49:18,580
 Ne mogu reći sada,

1259
00:49:18,580 --> 00:49:20,280
 sam nisam potpuno uklopio,

1260
00:49:20,280 --> 00:49:21,840
 nisam nikako uklopio,

1261
00:49:21,840 --> 00:49:24,140
 ali uvijek vidim te nekakve

1262
00:49:24,140 --> 00:49:26,060
 mini kulturalne šokove,

1263
00:49:26,060 --> 00:49:26,980
 kako bi ih nazvao,

1264
00:49:26,980 --> 00:49:28,180
 dakle u nekim stvarima.

1265
00:49:28,960 --> 00:49:31,320
 Život je u mnogo čemu drugčiji.

1266
00:49:31,320 --> 00:49:32,420
 Evo,

1267
00:49:32,420 --> 00:49:33,140
 taj Montreal,

1268
00:49:33,140 --> 00:49:33,860
 ako se ne varam,

1269
00:49:33,860 --> 00:49:35,840
 ima oko tri i po milijuna stanovnika

1270
00:49:35,840 --> 00:49:38,440
 sa nekakvim metropolitanskim područima.

1271
00:49:38,440 --> 00:49:39,080
 Kako cijera bejha.

1272
00:49:39,080 --> 00:49:39,580
 Da.

1273
00:49:39,580 --> 00:49:40,940
 I ovaj,

1274
00:49:40,940 --> 00:49:43,840
 u gradu je dosta promet,

1275
00:49:43,840 --> 00:49:45,100
 zna biti dosta ono,

1276
00:49:45,100 --> 00:49:45,900
 kako bih rekao,

1277
00:49:45,900 --> 00:49:47,760
