1282
00:49:55,720 --> 00:49:56,500
 kao kod nas,

1283
00:49:56,500 --> 00:49:56,820
 ono,

1284
00:49:56,820 --> 00:49:58,580
 u 10 minuta može sve obići,

1285
00:49:58,580 --> 00:49:59,960
 vidjeti 15 uvr glave.

1286
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:02,400
 Primjer se neki moji župljani žive

1287
00:50:02,400 --> 00:50:04,280
 i do dva sata od mene,

1288
00:50:04,280 --> 00:50:05,280
 je li to što je,

1289
00:50:05,280 --> 00:50:08,580
 što ti je apsolutno cijeli koncept

1290
00:50:08,580 --> 00:50:10,340
 tog pastoralnog djelovanja

1291
00:50:10,340 --> 00:50:12,320
 se mijenja.

1292
00:50:12,320 --> 00:50:14,600
 Ja sad mogu naravno govoriti

1293
00:50:14,600 --> 00:50:15,640
 neke svoje dojmove,

1294
00:50:15,640 --> 00:50:17,640
 koji su naravno već subjektivni.

1295
00:50:19,640 --> 00:50:21,500
 jer navikavam se na život u Kanadi,

1296
00:50:21,500 --> 00:50:22,640
 osobit u tom Montrealu,

1297
00:50:22,640 --> 00:50:24,600
 koji je poprilično hladan grad

1298
00:50:24,600 --> 00:50:26,660
 i ja sam baš dobio premještaj,

1299
00:50:26,660 --> 00:50:28,360
 ja to zovem već zima,

1300
00:50:28,360 --> 00:50:29,160
 iako ono,

1301
00:50:29,160 --> 00:50:30,700
 kao sezonski je bilo jesen,

1302
00:50:30,700 --> 00:50:31,860
 ali u biti je već bila zima,

1303
00:50:31,860 --> 00:50:33,700
 već temperature je bila ispod nule,

1304
00:50:33,700 --> 00:50:35,680
 ne baš da belo je ispod nule,

1305
00:50:35,680 --> 00:50:36,380
 ali bile su.

1306
00:50:36,380 --> 00:50:39,680
 Bude jako stvarno hladno

1307
00:50:39,680 --> 00:50:40,740
 i bude nekad,

1308
00:50:40,740 --> 00:50:42,860
 ono, mjeseci po dva dana

1309
00:50:42,860 --> 00:50:44,740
 gdje je temperatura non stop,

1310
00:50:44,740 --> 00:50:45,960
 ne znam,

1311
00:50:45,960 --> 00:50:47,360
 minus 10, minus 15,

1312
00:50:47,360 --> 00:50:48,780
 minus 20, minus 26,

1313
00:50:48,780 --> 00:50:49,160
 minus 20,

1314
00:50:49,160 --> 00:50:51,280
 to sam do te mjere primjesec,

1315
00:50:51,280 --> 00:50:52,080
 sad nedavno je sjećan,

1316
00:50:52,080 --> 00:50:52,920
 ne znam,

1317
00:50:52,920 --> 00:50:54,880
 5, 6 dana je bilo minus 26,

1318
00:50:54,880 --> 00:50:56,020
 ja ono,

1319
00:50:56,020 --> 00:50:57,660
 ja sam sa ovaj,

1320
00:50:57,660 --> 00:50:58,260
 kako se zove,

1321
00:50:58,260 --> 00:51:00,040
 zimogrozan ili zimogrizan,

1322
00:51:00,040 --> 00:51:00,740
 još uvijek ne znam,

1323
00:51:00,740 --> 00:51:01,860
 koja je točna riječ,

1324
00:51:01,860 --> 00:51:02,480
 ali ovaj,

1325
00:51:02,480 --> 00:51:03,340
 onda meni moji župljeni,

1326
00:51:03,340 --> 00:51:04,060
 neki stari govore,

1327
00:51:04,060 --> 00:51:04,840
 moj veličasni,

1328
00:51:04,840 --> 00:51:05,800
 ovo ti je ništa znalo,

1329
00:51:05,800 --> 00:51:06,620
 je biti do minus,

1330
00:51:06,620 --> 00:51:07,000
 ono,

1331
00:51:07,000 --> 00:51:07,740
 35,

1332
00:51:07,740 --> 00:51:08,120
 40,

1333
00:51:08,120 --> 00:51:09,100
 i tako dalje,

1334
00:51:09,100 --> 00:51:10,140
 onda ono,

1335
00:51:10,140 --> 00:51:10,660
 rekao dobro,

1336
00:51:10,660 --> 00:51:10,940
 evo,

1337
00:51:10,940 --> 00:51:11,220
 ajde.

1338
00:51:11,440 --> 00:51:12,600
 ovaj zima stvarno,

1339
00:51:12,600 --> 00:51:13,960
 neki koji su tamo dulje,

1340
00:51:13,960 --> 00:51:14,300
 kažu,

1341
00:51:14,300 --> 00:51:15,400
 bila je dosta duga,

1342
00:51:15,400 --> 00:51:16,600
 jer i meni je to,

1343
00:51:16,600 --> 00:51:18,580
 promjena mi je ogromna,

1344
00:51:18,580 --> 00:51:19,100
 naravno,

1345
00:51:19,100 --> 00:51:20,080
 mislim,

1346
00:51:20,080 --> 00:51:21,000
 banalna stvar,

1347
00:51:21,000 --> 00:51:22,180
 odete, ne znam,

