2112
01:11:17,780 --> 01:11:18,760
 I su žive vodi.

2113
01:11:18,760 --> 01:11:19,560
 Da, da.

2114
01:11:19,560 --> 01:11:22,000
 I zato tamo, na primjer,

2115
01:11:22,000 --> 01:11:24,140
