2128
01:11:41,700 --> 01:11:42,540
 mlađi svećenice,

2129
01:11:42,540 --> 01:11:43,680
 to je nedavno bilo istraživanje,

2130
01:11:43,680 --> 01:11:45,660
 sjećam se prije možda pola godine,

2131
01:11:45,660 --> 01:11:46,180
 tako nešto,

2132
01:11:46,180 --> 01:11:47,320
 tri, četiri mjeseca,

2133
01:11:47,320 --> 01:11:48,660
 da su mlađi svećenici,

2134
01:11:48,660 --> 01:11:49,440
 uvjetno rečeno,

2135
01:11:49,920 --> 01:11:50,960
 više tradicionalni,

2136
01:11:50,960 --> 01:11:53,680
 vidiš ti ovo ne pije više vode,

2137
01:11:53,680 --> 01:11:55,060
 ali mi to imamo,

2138
01:11:55,060 --> 01:11:55,560
 mi to,

2139
01:11:55,560 --> 01:11:55,900
 znaš,

2140
01:11:55,900 --> 01:11:57,080
 u nas se misla slavi,

2141
01:11:57,080 --> 01:11:58,360
 ja evo osobno,

2142
01:11:58,360 --> 01:11:59,320
 ja se ne mogu sjetiti,

2143
01:11:59,320 --> 01:12:00,280
 odrastao sam tu,

2144
01:12:00,280 --> 01:12:01,880
 da sam ikad bio na nekoj,

2145
01:12:01,880 --> 01:12:03,280
 am tako riješ nevaljanoj misi,

2146
01:12:03,280 --> 01:12:03,980
 ili misi koja,

2147
01:12:03,980 --> 01:12:06,460
 koja je bila puna nekakvih gluposti,

2148
01:12:06,580 --> 01:12:08,940
 mi smo jednostavno navikli da to je to,

2149
01:12:08,940 --> 01:12:09,340
 jeli,

2150
01:12:09,340 --> 01:12:09,880
 to je to,

2151
01:12:09,880 --> 01:12:10,140
 jeli,

2152
01:12:10,140 --> 01:12:11,740
 i ovaj,

2153
01:12:11,740 --> 01:12:12,940
 kako bih rekao,

2154
01:12:12,940 --> 01:12:14,060
 ima te obnove,

2155
01:12:14,060 --> 01:12:15,260
 Kanada opet,

2156
01:12:15,260 --> 01:12:16,760
 ja sam prekratko u Kanadi,

2157
01:12:16,760 --> 01:12:18,080
 za neki širi dojam,

2158
01:12:18,080 --> 01:12:19,480
 još samo sam u jednom gradu,

2159
01:12:19,480 --> 01:12:21,920
 nisam propovjedao na više nekih mjesta,

2160
01:12:21,920 --> 01:12:23,820
 pa ne mogu baš suditi,

2161
01:12:23,820 --> 01:12:25,600
