2200
01:13:38,720 --> 01:13:40,040
 da je to novi kontinent

2201
01:13:40,040 --> 01:13:42,580
 na koji ti moraš doći evangelizirati.

2202
01:13:43,700 --> 01:13:45,280
 Ja osobno mislim

2203
01:13:45,280 --> 01:13:47,800
