2299
01:16:18,820 --> 01:16:20,420
 iz samo te male skupine.

2300
01:16:20,420 --> 01:16:21,640
 A moram priznati

2301
01:16:21,640 --> 01:16:22,740
 da su oni više mene

2302
01:16:22,740 --> 01:16:23,520
 u nekom trenutku

2303
