2312
01:16:31,840 --> 01:16:32,540
 žele,

2313
01:16:32,540 --> 01:16:33,480
 troše se,

2314
01:16:33,480 --> 01:16:34,220
 daju se,

2315
01:16:34,220 --> 01:16:35,280
 i ja,

2316
