 kažem,

2317
01:16:35,800 --> 01:16:37,700
 smatram da imamo još više,

2318
01:16:37,700 --> 01:16:38,080
 naravno,

2319
01:16:38,080 --> 01:16:38,720
 prostora,

2320
01:16:38,720 --> 01:16:39,740
 ovaj,

2321
