 Evo,

2719
01:26:26,760 --> 01:26:28,720
 evo košta i sveti Franja,

2720
01:26:28,720 --> 01:26:30,300
 kako se za njega veže,

2721
01:26:30,300 --> 01:26:31,160
 ona rečenica,

2722
01:26:31,160 --> 01:26:32,740
 uvijek propovijedajte,

2723
01:26:32,740 --> 01:26:33,640
 ako je potrebno,

2724
01:26:33,640 --> 01:26:34,320
 koriste riječ.

2725
01:26:34,320 --> 01:26:35,100
 Koriste riječ.

2726
01:26:35,100 --> 01:26:36,420
 Da, ja

2727
01:26:36,420 --> 01:26:38,780
 ne mogu reći da

2728
