2743
01:26:53,220 --> 01:26:54,200
 ono,

2744
01:26:54,200 --> 01:26:55,600
 meni je draga tvoja radost.

2745
01:26:55,600 --> 01:26:56,280
 Evo,

2746
01:26:56,280 --> 01:26:57,040
 to je to,

2747
01:26:57,040 --> 01:26:58,800
 nisam ništa posebno rekao,

