2775
01:27:32,000 --> 01:27:33,000
 ljudskog u tebi,

2776
01:27:33,000 --> 01:27:33,460
 ono,

2777
01:27:33,460 --> 01:27:34,340
 kako bih rekao,

2778
01:27:34,340 --> 01:27:34,860
