2825
01:28:55,400 --> 01:28:56,640
 meni je samo ovaj važan svećnik,

2826
01:28:56,640 --> 01:28:57,540
 samo mi je ovaj drag svećnik,

2827
01:28:57,540 --> 01:28:58,220
 kao ovaj drugi ništa.

2828
01:28:58,220 --> 01:28:59,780
 Tu treba gledati vrlo široko.

2829
01:28:59,780 --> 01:29:00,820
 Ja sam se to uvjerio,

2830
01:29:00,820 --> 01:29:03,660
 kroz svoje franjevaštvo i život u samostanu.

2831
01:29:03,660 --> 01:29:06,180
 Ti imaš stvarno različitih fratara, likova,

2832
01:29:06,180 --> 01:29:09,140
 ali vidiš kako neki baš te stvar rade

2833
01:29:09,140 --> 01:29:10,600
 na jedan čudesan način.

2834
01:29:10,740 --> 01:29:12,520
 To treba priznati.

2835
01:29:12,520 --> 01:29:14,020
 To treba priznati, podržati.

2836
01:29:14,020 --> 01:29:14,600
 Dakle, nije,

2837
01:29:14,600 --> 01:29:16,860
 ok, naravno u nekom striktnom smislu

2838
01:29:16,860 --> 01:29:17,840
 i gospodin je tako rekao,

2839
01:29:17,840 --> 01:29:18,760
 idite po svijetu,

2840
01:29:18,760 --> 01:29:19,720
 propovjedajte vanđer,

2841
01:29:19,720 --> 01:29:20,220
 dakle, ok,

2842
01:29:20,220 --> 01:29:21,760
 imaš ideješ,

2843
01:29:21,760 --> 01:29:22,660
 nosiš iskustvo,

2844
01:29:22,660 --> 01:29:23,660
 nosiš riječi,

2845
01:29:23,660 --> 01:29:24,060
 riječ,

2846
01:29:24,060 --> 01:29:26,180
 kako se zove riječ,

2847
01:29:26,180 --> 01:29:26,600
 ovaj,

2848
01:29:26,600 --> 01:29:29,040
 dovodi do odnosa,

2849
01:29:29,040 --> 01:29:29,660
 apsolutno,

2850
01:29:30,240 --> 01:29:32,100
 ali isto tako ove neke druge stvari,

2851
01:29:32,100 --> 01:29:33,400
 ja sam upoznan ljudi,

2852
01:29:33,400 --> 01:29:38,420
 kad vidiš kako pristupaju potrebitima,

2853
01:29:38,420 --> 01:29:40,060
 kako pristupaju, ne znam,

2854
01:29:40,060 --> 01:29:42,860
 osobanost po teškoćama u razvoju,

2855
01:29:42,860 --> 01:29:45,500
 a kako pristupaju starijima nemoćnijima,

2856
01:29:45,500 --> 01:29:46,460
 ne treba,

2857
01:29:46,460 --> 01:29:47,960
 tu ti ne treba puno riječi.

2858
01:29:47,960 --> 01:29:49,500
 Dakle, samo taj pristup,

2859
01:29:49,500 --> 01:29:52,160
 ta blizina koju se osjeti,

2860
01:29:52,160 --> 01:29:54,980
 to srce koje oni imaju za tu neku osobu,

2861
01:29:54,980 --> 01:29:55,760
 to je genijalno.

2862
01:29:55,760 --> 01:29:57,360
 To je dobar dotiče ljudske duše.

2863
01:29:57,360 --> 01:29:59,540
 Da je upravo sani sveci primer,

2864
01:29:59,720 --> 01:30:01,060
