2867
01:30:07,500 --> 01:30:08,640
 sveci tome primjer.

2868
01:30:08,640 --> 01:30:11,680
 Evo kao što je Blažnji Karla Kutis kaže,

2869
01:30:11,680 --> 01:30:14,020
 svi smo mi rođeni kao originali,

2870
01:30:14,020 --> 01:30:16,860
 ali nažalost mnogi umiru kao kopjeo.

2871
01:30:16,860 --> 01:30:19,780
 Gdje mi ljudi nekako gubimo tu svoju autentičnost?

2872
01:30:19,780 --> 01:30:21,240
 Zašto je tako lako daje?

2873
01:30:21,240 --> 01:30:24,120
 To je baš dobro pitanje.

2874
01:30:24,120 --> 01:30:25,200
 To je super.

2875
01:30:25,200 --> 01:30:27,000
 Mislim da to je pitanje,

2876
01:30:27,000 --> 01:30:29,060
 baš baš se dobro to pitao,

2877
01:30:29,200 --> 01:30:30,620
 pogađa neki živac,

2878
01:30:30,620 --> 01:30:33,640
 pa uopćenito možda nekog danas,

2879
01:30:33,640 --> 01:30:36,400
 neke te vrlo široko svaće na autentičnosti,

2880
01:30:36,400 --> 01:30:38,660
 jednak ako svi, da se tako izrazimo u žargonu,

2881
01:30:38,660 --> 01:30:39,820
 briju na autentičnost,

2882
01:30:39,820 --> 01:30:42,540
 ali mnogi ovaj...

2883
01:30:42,540 --> 01:30:43,920
 Ja bih rekao da ima više razloga,

2884
01:30:43,920 --> 01:30:45,040
 moram prijateliti, malo si me zatekao,

2885
01:30:45,040 --> 01:30:46,060
 s pitanje, jako mi se sviđa,

2886
01:30:46,060 --> 01:30:46,920
 ali malo si me zatekao,

2887
01:30:46,920 --> 01:30:48,120
 pokušat ću ovako na prvu.

2888
01:30:48,120 --> 01:30:52,080
 Jedna od stvari gdje mi gubimo autentičnost je vjerojatno,

2889
01:30:52,080 --> 01:30:55,880
 su vjerojatno obziri.

2890
01:30:56,460 --> 01:30:58,240
 Dakle, mi smo ovdje,

2891
01:30:58,240 --> 01:30:59,660
 i ti ste odrasto i ja,

2892
01:30:59,660 --> 01:31:01,900
 nismo mi odrasto u nekom društvu

2893
01:31:01,900 --> 01:31:03,920
 koje šta god nešto novo,

2894
01:31:03,920 --> 01:31:08,240
 zanimljivo i što može baš donijeti dobre plodove,

2895
01:31:08,240 --> 01:31:09,880
 da su ljudi baš oduševljeni.

2896
01:31:10,240 --> 01:31:12,560
 Više je tu znak sumnje,

2897
01:31:12,560 --> 01:31:15,060
 više je tu nekakve,

2898
01:31:15,060 --> 01:31:17,300
 kako bih rekao ovaj,

2899
01:31:17,300 --> 01:31:19,220
 ne dostaje mi prava riječ,

2900
01:31:19,220 --> 01:31:20,020
 negodovanje,

2901
01:31:20,020 --> 01:31:21,420
 više je tu nekog negodovanja,

2902
01:31:21,420 --> 01:31:22,140
 malo sumnje,

2903
01:31:22,140 --> 01:31:24,140
 pa ajde, pa vidit ćemo,

2904
01:31:24,140 --> 01:31:25,100
 ili ono...

2905
01:31:25,100 --> 01:31:27,500
 Ljudi imaju neku najku i teško izgled za istot.

2906
01:31:27,500 --> 01:31:28,160
 Bravo, bravo.

2907
01:31:28,160 --> 01:31:30,180
 Dakle, ili onog krutog odbijanja,

2908
01:31:30,180 --> 01:31:32,380
 šta ćeš ti, šta ti, šta ti,

2909
01:31:32,380 --> 01:31:33,420
 i takve neke stvari.

2910
01:31:33,420 --> 01:31:35,780
 I onda, naravno mi,

2911
01:31:35,780 --> 01:31:37,800
 kao ranjiva, slaba ljudska bića,

2912
01:31:37,800 --> 01:31:39,620
 osobitno ako si malo emotivniji,

2913
01:31:39,720 --> 01:31:40,200
 i tako dalje,

2914
01:31:40,200 --> 01:31:41,900
 emocionalniji,

2915
01:31:41,900 --> 01:31:44,540
 ono, ili osjetljiviji na neki način,

2916
01:31:44,540 --> 01:31:46,580
 zbog ti obzira prestaneš,

2917
01:31:46,580 --> 01:31:48,100
 ono, izgubiš se negdje,

2918
01:31:48,100 --> 01:31:49,640
 i onda tražiš,

2919
01:31:49,640 --> 01:31:50,960
 možda kaže u amerikanci, fit,

2920
01:31:50,960 --> 01:31:54,020
 ono, tražiš da se s nekim uklopiš.

2921
01:31:54,020 --> 01:31:56,100
 To je najvjerojatno jasniji u srednjoj školi,

2922
01:31:56,100 --> 01:31:57,080
 kad uđeš u gimnaziju,

2923
01:31:57,080 --> 01:31:58,220
 neku drugu srednju školu,

2924
01:31:58,220 --> 01:32:00,580
 i onda, ono, imaš jednu facu nekog,

2925
01:32:00,580 --> 01:32:02,420
 nekog glavnog,

2926
01:32:02,420 --> 01:32:04,580
 i onda ovi drugi se nekako njemu priklanjaju,

2927
01:32:04,580 --> 01:32:05,620
 i tako dalje, jeli,

2928
01:32:09,720 --> 01:32:10,980
 njenjeni, poštovani, i tako dalje.

2929
01:32:10,980 --> 01:32:12,760
 Dakle, sigurno da tu ima tih,

2930
01:32:12,760 --> 01:32:15,180
 kako bih rekao, nekih velikih obzira.

2931
01:32:15,180 --> 01:32:18,260
 Nadalje, iskri ljena slika o samom sebi.

2932
01:32:18,260 --> 01:32:19,980
 Jel, mene, mene je to,

2933
01:32:19,980 --> 01:32:21,480
 ja ne krije,

2934
01:32:21,480 --> 01:32:22,740
 mene je to dugo močilo, jel.

2935
01:32:22,740 --> 01:32:24,960
 Ono, ja, naprijed, volim humor.

2936
01:32:24,960 --> 01:32:27,480
 Volim provaliti, volim neku šalu,

2937
01:32:27,480 --> 01:32:29,060
 nešto smiješno napraviti, tako dalje,

2938
01:32:29,060 --> 01:32:31,440
 a ja sam i mislal, ono, ne smiješ sad previše,

2939
01:32:31,440 --> 01:32:33,060
 znaš, ono, šta će ti ljudi reći,

2940
01:32:33,060 --> 01:32:35,220
 šta ti je fraterno, šta on sad,

2941
01:32:35,720 --> 01:32:38,940
 nastupa javno, sramotina, sramoti zajednicu,

2942
01:32:38,940 --> 01:32:41,520
 a ono, a u drugu ruku,

2943
01:32:41,520 --> 01:32:43,200
 svi smo željni prirodnosti,

2944
01:32:43,200 --> 01:32:45,000
 svi smo željni, da malo,

2945
01:32:45,000 --> 01:32:46,700
 jer život je sam po sebi težak,

2946
01:32:46,700 --> 01:32:49,340
 i taj humor nekad stvarno lakša,

2947
01:32:49,340 --> 01:32:52,580
 lakša, unese puno radosti, smijeha,

2948
01:32:52,580 --> 01:32:53,820
 ja, ono, nekad se, ono, punim,

2949
01:32:53,820 --> 01:32:55,360
 volim da smijat, i tako dalje,

2950
01:32:55,360 --> 01:32:57,260
 jer unese tu neku radost.

2951
01:32:57,260 --> 01:32:58,960
 I kad imaš, ovo što rekao,

2952
01:32:58,960 --> 01:33:01,500
 kad imaš iskrivnu sliku prema sebi,

2953
01:33:01,500 --> 01:33:03,160
 onda lakše, vjerojatno,

2954
01:33:03,720 --> 01:33:05,720
 pribjegavaš, kako bih rekao,

2955
01:33:05,720 --> 01:33:06,940
 pribjegavaš tim nekako,

2956
01:33:06,940 --> 01:33:07,840
 to je kopija.

2957
01:33:07,840 --> 01:33:08,500
 Evo primjen se danas,

2958
01:33:08,500 --> 01:33:10,700
 to je sjećanje kad sam bio baš u Americi,

2959
01:33:10,700 --> 01:33:12,440
 sad gledaš te srednjo školce,

2960
01:33:12,440 --> 01:33:14,880
 njih, bubam, devet od deset,

2961
01:33:14,880 --> 01:33:15,820
 ima istu frizuru,

2962
01:33:15,820 --> 01:33:16,860
 to ona, ono,

2963
01:33:16,860 --> 01:33:18,160
 ko ona, ko je vlas,

2964
01:33:18,160 --> 01:33:20,200
 ono, od kukuruza, ono, nešto,

2965
01:33:20,200 --> 01:33:20,920
 mislim,

2966
01:33:20,920 --> 01:33:22,600
 i svi imaju istu frizuru,

2967
01:33:22,600 --> 01:33:24,160
 a svak želi biti autentičan.

2968
01:33:24,160 --> 01:33:25,780
 Svi imaju iste objave,

2969
01:33:25,780 --> 01:33:27,220
 svi se isto oblače,

2970
01:33:27,220 --> 01:33:27,820
 svi imaju isto,

2971
01:33:27,820 --> 01:33:28,360
 je li, ono,

2972
01:33:29,140 --> 01:33:30,440
 i to je nekako, ono,

2973
01:33:30,440 --> 01:33:31,380
 okej, naravno,

2974
01:33:31,380 --> 01:33:33,220
 to je vrijeme neko traženja,

2975
01:33:33,220 --> 01:33:35,240
 jel, odlazaka na neku stranu,

2976
01:33:35,240 --> 01:33:36,180
 vraćanja, ono,

2977
01:33:36,180 --> 01:33:36,820
 back and forth,

2978
01:33:36,820 --> 01:33:38,500
 naprijed, nazad,

2979
01:33:38,500 --> 01:33:39,380
 i takve neke stvari,

2980
01:33:39,380 --> 01:33:40,500
 ali, ovaj,

2981
01:33:40,500 --> 01:33:41,780
 vjerujem da to isto,

2982
01:33:41,780 --> 01:33:42,660
 da to isto,

2983
01:33:42,660 --> 01:33:43,760
 da to isto utječe,

2984
01:33:43,760 --> 01:33:43,960
 je li,

2985
01:33:43,960 --> 01:33:45,640
 iskrivna slika,

2986
01:33:45,640 --> 01:33:46,500
 strahovi,

2987
01:33:46,500 --> 01:33:47,980
 kako će me ljudi participirati,

2988
01:33:47,980 --> 01:33:48,260
 je li,

2989
01:33:48,260 --> 01:33:48,880
 i tako dalje.

2990
01:33:49,000 --> 01:33:49,600
 sad nadalje,

2991
01:33:49,600 --> 01:33:51,160
 gdje se još izgubi,

2992
01:33:51,160 --> 01:33:53,500
 autentičnost možemo izgubiti,

2993
01:33:53,500 --> 01:33:56,180
 ako smo u nekom nezravom okruženju,

2994
01:33:56,180 --> 01:33:57,580
 to sigurno,

2995
01:33:57,580 --> 01:33:57,940
 jel,

2996
01:33:57,940 --> 01:33:59,400
 ne nožno okruženju,

2997
01:33:59,400 --> 01:34:00,500
 koje nas ne prihvaća,

2998
01:34:00,500 --> 01:34:00,820
 ali,

2999
01:34:00,820 --> 01:34:03,900
 koje nekako loše reagira na tu našu,

3000
01:34:03,900 --> 01:34:04,360
 ovaj,

3001
01:34:04,360 --> 01:34:06,000
 našu posebnost.

3002
01:34:06,000 --> 01:34:06,660
 Jer,

3003
01:34:06,660 --> 01:34:07,060
 realno,

3004
01:34:07,060 --> 01:34:09,240
 ovo što je Blažni Karlo kazao,

3005
01:34:09,240 --> 01:34:09,540
 dakle,

3006
01:34:09,540 --> 01:34:10,740
 mi stvarno jesmo,

3007
01:34:10,740 --> 01:34:12,100
 mi su svi posebni,

3008
01:34:12,100 --> 01:34:13,580
 sva čiji otisak prsta je drug čiji,

3009
01:34:13,580 --> 01:34:13,900
 dakle,

3010
01:34:13,900 --> 01:34:14,400
 to je,

3011
01:34:14,400 --> 01:34:15,420
 dakle,

3012
01:34:15,420 --> 01:34:16,280
 ono,

3013
01:34:16,960 --> 01:34:19,080
 autentično si već na neki način po rođenju,

3014
01:34:19,080 --> 01:34:20,100
 originalsi,

3015
01:34:20,100 --> 01:34:21,120
 svaki ima svoje denka.

3016
01:34:21,120 --> 01:34:21,440
 Tako,

3017
01:34:21,440 --> 01:34:23,180
 a moraš doći do svoje originalnosti,

3018
01:34:23,180 --> 01:34:23,740
 na neki način,

3019
01:34:23,740 --> 01:34:24,020
 dakle,

3020
01:34:24,020 --> 01:34:24,900
 odnosno,

3021
01:34:24,900 --> 01:34:26,140
 ekspresija,

3022
01:34:26,140 --> 01:34:27,980
 izričaj tvoje originalnosti,

3023
01:34:27,980 --> 01:34:29,460
 treba doći do toga.

3024
01:34:29,460 --> 01:34:30,220
 I,

3025
01:34:30,220 --> 01:34:30,620
 nažalost,

3026
01:34:30,620 --> 01:34:30,980
 nekad,

3027
01:34:30,980 --> 01:34:32,660
 možda osobit ovim,

3028
01:34:32,660 --> 01:34:34,380
 i našim manjim sredinama,

3029
01:34:34,380 --> 01:34:35,880
 ili nekim toksičnim sredinama,

3030
01:34:35,880 --> 01:34:39,420
 da su nekada neki ljudi iz neznanja i nerazumijevanja,

3031
01:34:39,420 --> 01:34:41,960
 ubili talento drugome.

3032
01:34:41,960 --> 01:34:43,020
 Doslovno ubili.

3033
01:34:43,420 --> 01:34:45,960
 Ubili autentičnost u nekim drugim,

3034
01:34:45,960 --> 01:34:49,600
 u osobitom možda u mladima i tako dalje.

3035
01:34:49,600 --> 01:34:50,900
 On nekako se i baš srezali,

3036
01:34:50,900 --> 01:34:51,140
 jel?

3037
01:34:51,140 --> 01:34:52,360
 Što,

3038
01:34:52,360 --> 01:34:54,000
 što po meni,

3039
01:34:54,000 --> 01:34:54,900
 nažalost,

3040
01:34:54,900 --> 01:34:55,460
 nije mislim,

3041
01:34:55,460 --> 01:34:56,460
 ono,

3042
01:34:56,460 --> 01:34:57,540
 to mi je ko u nogomet.

3043
01:34:57,540 --> 01:34:59,260
 Ako hoćeš,

3044
01:34:59,260 --> 01:35:00,460
 između ostalog,

3045
01:35:00,460 --> 01:35:01,320
 zabiti gol,

3046
01:35:01,320 --> 01:35:01,640
 naravno,

3047
01:35:01,640 --> 01:35:02,540
 možeš našta načina,

3048
01:35:02,540 --> 01:35:02,740
 ali,

3049
01:35:02,740 --> 01:35:05,940
 moraš znati i dati loptu u prostor,

3050
01:35:05,940 --> 01:35:07,700
 moraš znati čuvati prostora

3051
01:35:07,700 --> 01:35:10,140
 i otvarati prostor za druge igrače.

3052
01:35:10,140 --> 01:35:12,540
 To mi se čini jako važnijim.

3053
01:35:12,540 --> 01:35:14,860
 Kad vidiš da je neko ima

3054
01:35:14,860 --> 01:35:15,640
 neki talent,

3055
01:35:15,640 --> 01:35:16,400
 neki dar,

3056
01:35:16,400 --> 01:35:18,380
 otvorimo prostor,

3057
01:35:18,380 --> 01:35:21,300
 dadi mu loptu da uđe unutra

3058
01:35:21,300 --> 01:35:22,840
 i da on može zaviti,

3059
01:35:22,840 --> 01:35:23,980
 onda svi slavimo.

3060
01:35:23,980 --> 01:35:24,520
 Jer,

3061
01:35:24,520 --> 01:35:25,480
 nerijedko,

3062
01:35:25,480 --> 01:35:25,680
 evo,

3063
01:35:25,680 --> 01:35:27,360
 baš kad je neko stvarno talentiran,

3064
01:35:27,360 --> 01:35:29,000
 kad ima mnoge lijepe darove

3065
01:35:29,000 --> 01:35:30,520
 i koje dijeli drugima

3066
01:35:30,520 --> 01:35:32,120
 i na taj način služi drugima,

3067
01:35:32,120 --> 01:35:33,180
 svi se radujemo.

3068
01:35:33,180 --> 01:35:33,680
 Evo,

3069
01:35:33,680 --> 01:35:34,260
 ja se,

3070
01:35:34,260 --> 01:35:35,320
 kad čitam neke,

3071
01:35:35,320 --> 01:35:35,600
 naprijed,

3072
01:35:35,600 --> 01:35:35,920
 knjige,

3073
01:35:35,920 --> 01:35:36,640
 neke pise,

3074
01:35:36,640 --> 01:35:37,480
 književnike,

3075
01:35:37,480 --> 01:35:38,040
 dakle,

3076
01:35:38,040 --> 01:35:39,440
 njemu je to dano.

3077
01:35:39,440 --> 01:35:41,360
 A ja radostana nikada nisam upoznao.

3078
01:35:41,360 --> 01:35:41,620
 Dakle,

3079
01:35:41,620 --> 01:35:42,860
 to je vrlo važno.

3080
01:35:42,860 --> 01:35:44,720
 I možda zadnje što mi sad pada,

3081
01:35:44,720 --> 01:35:45,140
 kažem,

3082
01:35:45,140 --> 01:35:45,940
 zatekao si me,

3083
01:35:45,940 --> 01:35:47,260
 ali jako je dobro pitanje.

3084
01:35:47,260 --> 01:35:49,420
 Možda zadnje što mi pada na pamet,

3085
01:35:49,420 --> 01:35:50,980
 čini mi se

3086
01:35:50,980 --> 01:35:52,100
 da smo,

3087
01:35:53,560 --> 01:35:55,100
 možda i ovom ovdje kontekstu,

3088
01:35:55,100 --> 01:35:56,200
 a možda općenito

3089
01:35:56,200 --> 01:35:57,040
 i društvene mreža

3090
01:35:57,040 --> 01:35:57,900
 su tome pomogle,

3091
01:35:57,900 --> 01:35:59,140
 čini mi se

3092
01:35:59,140 --> 01:35:59,800
 da smo došli

3093
01:35:59,800 --> 01:36:01,340
 do vrlo alarmantne razine

3094
01:36:01,340 --> 01:36:02,840
 zavisti i ljubomore.

3095
01:36:02,840 --> 01:36:07,140
 I da baš i zavisti i ljubomore

3096
01:36:07,140 --> 01:36:08,580
 mnogi ljudi,

3097
01:36:08,580 --> 01:36:08,960
 jednostavno,

3098
01:36:08,960 --> 01:36:11,100
 koji bi trebali nekako izaći

3099
01:36:11,100 --> 01:36:11,700
 u javnost,

3100
01:36:11,700 --> 01:36:12,900
 dođi na svjetlo dana,

3101
01:36:12,900 --> 01:36:14,560
 da nemaju pristupa.

3102
01:36:14,560 --> 01:36:15,840
 Što zbog toga što znaju

3103
01:36:15,840 --> 01:36:16,700
 da će neko biti zavidan,

3104
01:36:16,700 --> 01:36:16,980
 pa ono,

3105
01:36:16,980 --> 01:36:17,620
 aj, neću,

3106
01:36:17,620 --> 01:36:18,680
 ne želim njima,

3107
01:36:18,680 --> 01:36:20,020
 nešto kao da ispada

3108
01:36:23,560 --> 01:36:25,420
 baš marginalizirati

3109
01:36:25,420 --> 01:36:27,940
 samo zato što ti imaš nešto

3110
01:36:27,940 --> 01:36:29,180
 što neko drugi nema.

3111
01:36:29,180 --> 01:36:30,580
 Nažalost,

3112
01:36:30,580 --> 01:36:31,840
 to čini mi se,

3113
01:36:31,840 --> 01:36:33,280
 jer društvene mreže hrane

3114
01:36:33,280 --> 01:36:33,780
 je zavisti,

3115
01:36:33,780 --> 01:36:34,620
 definitivno,

3116
01:36:34,620 --> 01:36:36,200
 Instagram pogotovo,

3117
01:36:36,200 --> 01:36:37,240
